    Benchmarking ‘collections’

    benchmark.Rmd

    The goal of this document is to compare the performances of some of the existing packages. See benchmark.Rmd for the details.

    We are comparing these packages with collections.

    • dequer 2.0-1
    • datastructures 0.2.5
    • liqueueR 0.0.1
    • hash 2.2.6
    • hashmap 0.2.2

    Queue

    microbenchmark(
    dequer = test_dequer_queue_push_pop(200),
    datastructures = test_datastructures_queue_push_pop(200),
    liqueueR = test_liqueueR_queue_push_pop(200),
    collections = test_collections_queue_push_pop(200),
    times = 10,
    unit = "relative"
)
    ## Unit: relative
##            expr   min    lq   mean median    uq    max neval
##          dequer  1.00  1.00   1.00   1.00  1.00   1.00    10
##  datastructures  8.47  9.05 127.50   9.06  8.35 263.59    10
##        liqueueR 12.95 13.88   8.99  14.16 12.34   4.09    10
##     collections  2.03  2.03   1.81   1.95  2.20   1.50    10
    microbenchmark(
    dequer = test_dequer_queue_push_pop(2000),
    datastructures = test_datastructures_queue_push_pop(2000),
    liqueueR = test_liqueueR_queue_push_pop(2000),
    collections = test_collections_queue_push_pop(2000),
    times = 10,
    unit = "relative"
)
    ## Unit: relative
##            expr  min   lq mean median   uq  max neval
##          dequer 1.42 1.56 1.72   1.57 1.65 2.92    10
##  datastructures 4.05 4.16 3.98   4.09 3.85 3.74    10
##        liqueueR 8.66 9.27 8.76   9.06 8.44 8.32    10
##     collections 1.00 1.00 1.00   1.00 1.00 1.00    10

    Deque

    microbenchmark(
    dequer = test_dequer_deque_push_pop(200),
    collections = test_collections_deque_push_pop(200),
    times = 10,
    unit = "relative"
)
    ## Unit: relative
##         expr  min   lq mean median   uq  max neval
##       dequer 1.00 1.00 1.00   1.00 1.00 1.00    10
##  collections 2.76 2.75 1.94   2.88 2.22 1.44    10
    microbenchmark(
    dequer = test_dequer_deque_push_pop(2000),
    collections = test_collections_deque_push_pop(2000),
    times = 10,
    unit = "relative"
)
    ## Unit: relative
##         expr  min  lq mean median   uq  max neval
##       dequer 1.00 1.0 1.00   1.00 1.00 1.00    10
##  collections 1.42 1.3 1.26   1.24 1.24 1.13    10
    microbenchmark(
    dequer = test_dequer_deque_push_pop(20000),
    collections = test_collections_deque_push_pop(20000),
    times = 10,
    unit = "relative"
)
    ## Unit: relative
